{"id": 2631, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得生活中关于「变老」的哪些说法，其实是有问题的？", "description": "欢迎列举你心中「当自己老了之后，最害怕得到的评价」。（题图来自：iStock ©️ jesadaphorn）", "record_count": 3022, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181119164412ubGck3BoaASvRnKx.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-26T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 313601, "content": "冬天我要穿加绒裤子鞋子和袄子，年轻人一个个还在露着脚踝穿着卫衣", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1517156}, {"id": 313606, "content": "并不是年纪大了就算老了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1517183}, {"id": 313610, "content": "老是有别人拿不一定适合我的惯例来要求我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1517165}, {"id": 313355, "content": "别人:不打游戏，不熬夜，不刷抖音，爱健身。你的生活有什么乐趣？你这是要提前过上老年生活吗？\n我:？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？\n内心mmp，老子才二十岁！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516280}, {"id": 313356, "content": "生活方式的不同，不能被人当做年老的把柄。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516280}, {"id": 313613, "content": "认为老了就没有性生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327849}, {"id": 313615, "content": "全部都有问题，不用赞了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 72294}, {"id": 314127, "content": "谢谢阿姨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290331}, {"id": 313361, "content": "不敢放手，也不敢拥抱的爱情", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516290}, {"id": 314642, "content": "变老就得成家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1523082}, {"id": 315666, "content": "老牛吃嫩草，请别用恶意去揣测感情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527871}, {"id": 314137, "content": "七岁看老", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1520406}, {"id": 318491, "content": "没事儿就老了老了其实只不过是懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538092}, {"id": 315425, "content": "其他人：看照片里的你有30多岁了吧！\n我：🙄(内心：老子不美颜不修图就这么被歧视？)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962238}, {"id": 313122, "content": "老了就会对很多事情不感兴趣\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1483822}, {"id": 313123, "content": "30岁便是阿姨", "image": null, "praise_count": 259, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1229406}, {"id": 313124, "content": "好丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1376150}, {"id": 313125, "content": "老了，就要随波逐流？", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1388915}, {"id": 313129, "content": "年轻人忘了点事情，就自嘲说我老了，其实日子还长要忘的多着呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1447806}, {"id": 313130, "content": "守旧\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932193}, {"id": 313131, "content": "“都这个年纪了，还捯饬么啊”\n我有年龄≠我不要形象OK👌?", "image": null, "praise_count": 245, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513278}, {"id": 313132, "content": "老了就不用自律?", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512557}, {"id": 313133, "content": "思想陈旧，跟不上时代", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1491405}, {"id": 313134, "content": "你肯定不懂\n我们有代沟了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1515036}, {"id": 314670, "content": "想买个平底锅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352052}, {"id": 313135, "content": "孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1330659}, {"id": 313647, "content": "老了=我不用学习任何知识=我不会做这些理所应当=我可以耗着日子等待退休享清福", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454283}, {"id": 313136, "content": "老了就上公交必须有座？", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1471633}, {"id": 313137, "content": "用生理年龄判断是否老去", "image": null, "praise_count": 65, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514401}, {"id": 313138, "content": "无家可归", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1330659}, {"id": 313139, "content": "都30岁了，还看动漫，玩游戏？拜托。看动漫和玩游戏跟年纪又半毛钱关系吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 391, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238342}, {"id": 313907, "content": "秃发少女", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1518712}, {"id": 313140, "content": "“你肯定听不懂的”", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1503575}, {"id": 313141, "content": "在我们国家，好多事情好像是为了你这个年纪而量身定做的。来自父母的灵魂拷问，都25了，女朋友呢？都27,8了还不结婚？都30岁了，还不要孩子？34了，还不要二胎？\r\n来自媳妇的灵魂拷问，都30了，什么时候能有第二套房子？都结婚好几年了，什么时候买车？你到底多少岁能成功变的有钱？", "image": null, "praise_count": 189, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238342}, {"id": 313653, "content": "喜欢的东西和一颗年轻的心好像就应该随着年纪的改变而顺势改变，每个阶段该做什么事好像都被安排的明明白白", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516647}, {"id": 313143, "content": "倚老卖老", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1349071}, {"id": 313144, "content": "“是我老了吗？都听不懂现在的孩子在说什么”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319214}, {"id": 313145, "content": "20岁已经被叫做老阿姨😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475046}, {"id": 313147, "content": "大学毕业就是老了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1430035}, {"id": 313148, "content": "20多岁与小几岁的沟通，老阿姨跟不上你们这些小年轻的步伐", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314980}, {"id": 313149, "content": "什么老母亲、老父亲之类的，明明都是三十多岁的人……，真不理解，不是都说自己还是宝宝么，反差也太大了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050868}, {"id": 313150, "content": "经常拿女性的年龄来说事，说年龄和女性价值成反比，这些人就是脑壳有包", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054974}, {"id": 313151, "content": "老了就不会再热爱游戏了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455119}, {"id": 313152, "content": "变丑不是老了，而且你本来就是这么丑", "image": "img/option/option/20181126121208lnJEBb5uKOyZwChT", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278578}, {"id": 313153, "content": "30左右就说自己老了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446282}, {"id": 313154, "content": "很多事情因为老了就懒得计较", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1515112}, {"id": 313156, "content": "老阿姨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1515123}, {"id": 313157, "content": "你孩子都这么大了，你还……！\n\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1515131}, {"id": 313158, "content": "“年轻”不是你们努力争取的成果，“老”也不是因为我做错什么而得到的惩罚。\n\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1515133}, {"id": 313414, "content": "不顾身材吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516468}]}